net.sf.tweety.action.description

Class CActionDescription

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.tweety.commons.BeliefSet<T>
      • net.sf.tweety.action.ActionDescription<CLaw>
        • net.sf.tweety.action.description.CActionDescription
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<CLaw>, Collection<CLaw>, net.sf.tweety.commons.BeliefBase

    public class CActionDescription
extends ActionDescription<CLaw>
    This class represents an action description for the action language C as a set of causal rules, and provides some basic functionality such as grounding.
    Author:
    Sebastian Homann
